      "Select the optimal model based on task requirements such as typography, photorealism, or speed",
      "Handle multilingual in-image text rendering with GPT Image 2 for headlines and posters",
      "Process batch operations for concept ideation using 4-up parallel generation",
      "Support open-weights and LoRA workflows for custom model deployments"
