      {
        "question": "Do I need to install anything to use this skill?",
        "answer": "Yes, you need the RunComfy CLI. Install it with npm i -g @runcomfy/cli and authenticate with runcomfy login or by setting the RUNCOMFY_TOKEN environment variable."
